body.description: Travel confidently with the Duo-Tone Collection from IT Luggage. The aluminum trolley system helps to minimize the weight while maximizing strength as you glide to your destination on an 8-wheel rolling system offering excellent control and maneuverability. The large outer pockets allow easy access to your most essential travel items while the spacious lined interior means you can pack more in on your next journey. The padded top and side handle make travel a breeze and with a 10-year warranty you are assured quality in every suitcase. The Duo-Tone collection is going to make your next trip a seamless one.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Our story For nearly 40 we have focused on designing luggage that meets the travel needs of our customers. Our focus has and always will remain on our founding principles – Design, Innovation, Quality and Value. Back in the early days, we started as luggage importers, at that time luggage was bland, boxy, and generally black, BORING! and this is when the vision was born, what if we designed it ourselves? We could approach suitcase design a bit differently, sure it's functional but can’t it be beautiful yet affordable too? What if we started with color and inspiring designs? What if the breadth of our offering gave customers real choice? What if we did all this but through clever design, development, purchasing, and excellent supply chain relationships, and as they say, the rest is history, it luggage’s history.

reviews.reviewText: This spinner wheeled carry on was perfect for a recent trip to Europe. It fit in the overhead compartments and was easy to maneuver. It is one large compartment with a zipper inner flap and 2 outer compartments. The outer compartments fit my 8X12" papers and a book in the larger compartment and an small umbrella in the other compartment. If you need more separation of your items, you can use cubes.
